      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, what do you mean by \"rogue band of goblins\"? I'm just asking about atmospheric physics. Can we stick to the technical side? How exactly does the interaction between the jet stream and the surrounding air create those specific shear zones?",
      "source": "evaluator"
